itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson, Dan Hollaway, and Jessie Wiseman wrap up the week with the realest fake news including a man whose farts kill mosquitoes who was hired to create mosquito repellant made from his intestinal gas, Greta Thunberg being named "Time" magazine's person of the year, the pest controllers in New York who accidentally created a new breed of 'super rat', the former NBA player who was fined for not showing proper respect to China Flag, Harvey Weinstein reaches $25M settlement with his victims, Don Lemon left speechless after Trump's Thanos meme, and how the Monmouth and Quinnipiac polls show Americans don’t support impeachment.
